{"tid":2013318,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強把警隊捧上天 稱警員與「上帝」齊名","createTime":"2020-05-12T08:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T10:36:03.000Z","uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"84881e13f445390e5942918e065bf76ddfb7b6d7","tid":2013318,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:20:39.000Z","msg":"褻瀆（英語：Blasphemy），又稱冒瀆，是指對上帝、神靈、宗教上的神話人物、書籍或聖物，作出侮辱的行為，發表批評或負面的言論，或是展現出缺少敬意、輕視的態度。在某些宗教中，認為褻瀆是一種宗教上的罪行，如基督教與回教。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強開場發言指，期望區議會並非只作政治表態及單方面謾罵，指希望作理性討論。他提到近期有警員相繼被捕，重申對於內部出現「害群之馬」感可惜，「褻瀆神聖身份」。"},{"pid":"ef96b7ae91a9452d62d0a5882010c7782a090fce","tid":2013318,"uid":309553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/562359/org/8295aabe44a678d430438b629ff402c2.jpg/GV0rOt74cFI5BVMi8MQwQZQTRV9IphPLFX4n2hV-J9o?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F562359%2Forg%2F8295aabe44a678d430438b629ff402c2.jpg%2FGV0rOt74cFI5BVMi8MQwQZQTRV9IphPLFX4n2hV-J9o%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=c4be69f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"023f7fceedb8eb2ecbeb5af147373aa4ad8d2f37","tid":2013318,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:27:02.000Z","msg":"咁3萬隻打算幾時上十字架啊 我地好樂意幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062b005ae51fc579810d310108a80c8797697188","tid":2013318,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:31:42.000Z","msg":"佢想做上帝個老豆<br />\n<br />\n呢種人自大到脹爆"},{"pid":"6c830e46956ee41de6783edabe454f56dc464d76","tid":2013318,"uid":180851,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"成個社會最垃圾 一事無成既先做<br />\n讀唔成書就毅進 再入警隊<br />\n入到u既 9成都係垃圾科先去考督察<br />\n<br />\n入去受訓個幾個月出來<br />\n你唔係以為會變左咩偉人 正人君子出來呀麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n垃圾幾時都係垃圾"},{"pid":"94bf86